They reproduce faster than rabbits do. They all claim to be the one. I'm talking about machine learning courses. I want to promote one that I consider particularly good. It is FREE, no ads, no option to buy paid certificates, ABSOLUTELY NO MONETIZATION involved. It is just knowledge sharing for the sake of sharing knowledge.

The course is http://course.fast.ai/

The blog is also soething worth reading once in a while: http://fast.ai/
